<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='310000' id='t-310000'>And if we look at a very pristine environment like western Australia,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='313000' id='t-313000'>Lars Bider has done work</span>
