<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='321000' id='t-321000'>When there was one boat, not much of an impact.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='324000' id='t-324000'>And two boats: When the second boat was added,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='327000' id='t-327000'>what happened was that some of the dolphins</span>
