<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='364000' id='t-364000'>And I'd like to switch now from this local,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='366000' id='t-366000'>familiar, coastal environment</span>
