<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411000' id='t-411000'>So we live in a world of satellite communication,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>are used to global communication,</span>
